<div class="content">
      </br>
      <h2 class="content-head is-center">Log in to play a game.</h2>

      <div class="pure-g">
          <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-5">

        <%=  form_tag("/login", method: "POST") do %>
          <%=  label_tag(:email, "Email") %>
          <%= text_field_tag(:email) %>

          <%=  label_tag(:password, "Password") %>
          <%= password_field_tag(:password) %>

          <%= submit_tag("Login") %>
        <% end %>


            <h4>Don't have an account?</h4>
              <form class="pure-form pure-form-stacked">
                <fieldset>
                    <a class="pure-button" href="/signup">Sign Up!</a>
                </fieldset>
              </form>
          </div>

      <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
          <h4>More about the game</h4>
          <p>
              It's a twist on Truth Or Dare. Once you log-in, you'll have an option to play a randomly generated truth or dare game or you can play a game made by a friend. You'll post a bounty to play. Once the bounty is paid, you'll see a truth or a dare. Should you choose to accept and complete one of the challenges, you'll get a reward. If you chicken-out, then your bounty is donated to a charity of your choice.
          </p>

          <h4>Contact Us</h4>
          <p>
              If you have any questions, please send us an email at <a href="mailto:hello@basilinda.com" target="_top">hello@basilinda.com</a>.
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


